{"name":"Doll-Creation (Su) part 1","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"doll-creation\"><strong>Doll-Creation (Su)</strong></h3><p>At 1st level, the dollmaker gains <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/item-creation-feats/craft-poppet-item-creation/\">Craft Poppet </a>as a bonus feat and may modify Animated Dolls with augmentations. In addition, the dollmaker gains a +1 competence bonus to Craft (Carpentry) and Craft (Sculpting) checks, plus an additional +1 bonus per two necromancer levels after 1st.</p><p>This ability replaces spell proficiency and secrets of the dead.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#doll-creation\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><hr><p>Make sure to add the correct feat as this just adds a bonus feat.</p><p>Make sure both skill bonuses under changes have been moved to the correct skill</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[{"_id":"IjdSNUwl","formula":"1","operator":"add","subTarget":"bonusFeats","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"GsOgqQcS","formula":"floor((@classes.necromancer.level+1)/2)","operator":"add","subTarget":"skill.crf","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"i926O9bC","formula":"floor((@classes.necromancer.level+1)/2)","operator":"add","subTarget":"skill.crf","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Necroman