{"name":"Limit Break: Forbidden Grimoire (Su)","type":"buff","img":"icons/svg/ice-aura.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Forbidden Grimoire (Su): </em>The dollmaker targets a friendly Construct within 30 feet under his control and suffuse it with truly heinous dark magicks to “Perfect” his creation. The construct gains 1d8 temporary + 1d8 per four necromancer levels after 1st, as well as a +4 circumstance bonus to its primary and secondary scores for 1 round + 1 round per four necromancer levels after 1st. This limit break replaces requires only a swift action.</span></p><p>This limit break requires only a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#swift\">swift action </a>.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif\">This ability replaces the Limit Break (Grasp of The Dead).</span></p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><hr><p>Instructions for setup</p><p>set level to that of the duration of the limit break</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[{"_id":"2iO1xhaL","formula":"4","operator":"add","subTarget":"cha","modifier":"circumstance","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"XklrlDUB","formula":"4","operator":"add","subTarget":"dex","modifier":"circumstance","priority