{"name":"Phantasmal Strings (Su)","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"phantasmal-strings\"><strong>Phantasmal Strings (Su)</strong></h3><p>At 1st level, as a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#standard\">standard action </a>, a dollmaker can infuse a construct creature within 30 feet with shadow energy. It gains a +1 profane bonus on all attack rolls and saving throws, as well as 1 temporary hit point per Hit Die and a +10 bonus to its movement speed. The bonus on attack rolls and saving throws increases by +1 for every five necromancer levels he possesses. These bonuses last for a number of rounds equal to half his necromancer level (minimum 1 round). He can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + his Intelligence modifier.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_necromancer.iq4Q3mo3xy3DfMUk]{Phantasmal Strings (Su)}</p><p>This ability replaces bolster.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#phantasmal-strings\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><p>Set buff level to that of the Dollmaker's class level</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"1U5oY3RcIy1sY5SO","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard","unchained":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"max(1,floor(@classes.necromancer.level/2))","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":""}},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttack