{"_id":"8K38DPI7OSfYsOCw","name":"Necromancy Talent, Adv: Transfer Spell*","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The necromancer can cast some spells with a range of &ldquo;personal&rdquo; and a target of &ldquo;you&rdquo; as if they had a range of &ldquo;touch&rdquo; and a target of &ldquo;1 willing creature.&rdquo; Only spells that do not increase the target&rsquo;s attack bonus or armor class and have a duration longer than 1 round may be cast in this way. The necromancer can only use this talent on spells with a spell level no greater than half of the highest level spell the necromancer knows. The necromancer may use this ability a total number of times per day equal to 3 + his Charisma modifier.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Advanced Necromancy Talent"],"actions":[{"_id":"dsiVHMrKB5pz5Es2","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special","unchained":{"cost":1,"type":"special"}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"day","value":0,"maxFormula":"3+@abilities.cha.mod","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":null,"attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":""},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":[],"attackNotes":[],"soundEffect":"","powerAttack":{"multiplier":"","damageBonus":2,"critMultiplier":1},"naturalAttack":{"primaryAttack":true,"secondary":{"attackBonus":"-5","damageMult":0.5}},"nonlethal":false,"touch":