{"_id":"AkYVGwYa9wj3k64X","name":"Bolster (Su)","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"bolster\">Bolster (<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#supernatural\">Su</a>)</h3><p>At 1st level, as a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#standard\">move action </a>, a necromancer can infuse an undead creature within 30 feet with shadow energy. It gains a +1 profane bonus on all attack rolls and saving throws, as well as 1 temporary hit point per Hit Die and a +2 bonus to its turn resistance. The bonus on attack rolls and saving throws increases by +1 for every five necromancer levels he possesses. These bonuses last for a number of minutes equal to his necromancer level. He can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + his Charisma modifier.</p><p>Bonus to attack and saving throws: [[1+floor(@classes.necromancer.level/5)]]</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#bolster\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_necromancer.ceweSXq7iIzki3Dk]{Bolster (Su)}</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"gzqBAQq6oCjL8oIM","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard","unchained":{"cost":2,"type":"action"}},"duration":{"value":"max(1,floor(@classes.necromancer.level/2))","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"30","units":"ft","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":""},"per":"day","value":0,"maxFormula":"3+@abilites.cha.mod","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critPart