{"name":"Grand Guignol (Su)","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"grand-guignol\"><strong>Grand Guignol (Su)</strong></h3><p>At 9th level, the dollmaker attains the ability to float upon phantasmal strings as he walks, gaining the effects of <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/f/float/\">Float </a>for as long as the dollmaker wills it. In addition, his constructs that he is connected with Phantasmal Strings can attain the effects of <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/f/fly/\">Fly </a>for 1 minute.</p><p>This ability replaces miasma.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#grand-guignol\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Necromancer"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":false,"prf":false,"pil":false,"pro":false,"rep":false,"rid":false,"sen":false,"slt":false,"spl":false,"ste":false,"sur":false,"swm":false,"umd":false},"currency":{"pp":{},"