{"name":"Perfected Creations (Su)","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"perfected-creations\"><strong>Perfected Creations (Su)</strong></h3><p>At 11th level, the dollmaker’s constructs have entered their finalized form, his constructs gain +4 to Charisma and Dexterity and +2 additional HP per hit die.</p><p>This ability replaces undead mastery.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#perfected-creations\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><p>Player will need to make the adjustments to their dolls.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":""},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Necromancer"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":false,"clm":false,"crf":false,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kdu":false,"ken":false,"kge":false,"khi":false,"klo":false,"kna":false,"kno":false,"kpl":false,"kre":false,"kte":false,"lin":false,"nav":false,"per":false,"prf":false,"pil":false,"pro":false,"rep":false,"rid":false,"sen":false,"slt":false,"spl":false,"ste":false,"sur":false,"swm":false,"umd":false},"currency":{"pp":{},"gp":{},"sp":{},"cp":{}},"altCurrency":{"pp":{},"gp":{},"sp":{},"cp":{}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_5rvqcvuuap"}},