{"_id":"XUvjS3M8P3GWxEte","name":"Necromancy Talent: Defile","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Necromancer 6, Harm Touch class feature</p>\n<hr />\n<p>The necromancer gains one defile from the dark knight&rsquo;s 3rd-level defile list. At 12th level, the necromancer gains one defile from the dark knight&rsquo;s 6th-level defile list. At 18th level, the necromancer gains one defile from the dark knight&rsquo;s 9th-level defile list. The necromancer uses his necromancer level as his dark knight level.</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Necromancy Talent"],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":["Necromancer"]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"ability":{"damageMult":1,"critMult":2}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.4","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1667698089420,"modifiedTime":1694209595643,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_d5gviacy7vl"}}}
{"_id":"YxXjY3pobQU1j66S","name":"Unlife Healer (Su)","type":"feat","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/skills/ice_17.jpg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"unlife-healer\">Unlife Healer (<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#supernatural\">Su</a>)</h3><p>At 8th level, the necromancer’s spells, spell-like abilities, and supernatural abilities used to heal undead gain the benefit of the <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/feats/metamagic-feats/empower-spell/\">Empower Spell </a>feat. At 16th level, these effects also gain the benefit of the <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/feats/metamagic-feats/maximize-spell/\">Maximize Spell </a>feat.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#unlife-healer\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":["Spells"],"actions":[{"_id":"bBACJpBNJin4Lq9c","name":"Use","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/skills/ice_17.jpg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special","unchained":{"cost":1,"type":"special"}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"","value":0,"maxFormula":"","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":null,"attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":""},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":[],"attackNotes":[],"soundEffect":"","powerAttack":{"multiplier":"","damageBonus":2,"critMultiplier":1},"naturalAttack":{"primaryAttack":tru