{"name":"Bolster (Su)","type":"buff","img":"icons/svg/ice-aura.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"bolster\">Bolster (<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#supernatural\">Su</a>)</h3><p>At 1st level, as a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#standard\">move action </a>, a necromancer can infuse an undead creature within 30 feet with shadow energy. It gains a +1 profane bonus on all attack rolls and saving throws, as well as 1 temporary hit point per Hit Die and a +2 bonus to its turn resistance. The bonus on attack rolls and saving throws increases by +1 for every five necromancer levels he possesses. These bonuses last for a number of minutes equal to his necromancer level. He can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + his Charisma modifier.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/#bolster\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[{"_id":"oKvmLFnI","formula":"@item.level","operator":"add","subTarget":"attack","modifier":"profane","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"oGWC7LSt","formula":"@item.level","operator":"add","subTarget":"allSavingThrows","modifier":"profane","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"temp","active":false,"level":1,"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"hideFromToken":false,"uses":{"per":""}},"ownership":{"default":0,"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_mlzefn8ai9d"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.7","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1708297558087,"modifiedTime":1708912733914,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"_id":"ceweSXq7iIzki3Dk"}
{"name":"Guignol (Su)","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"guignol\"><strong>Guignol (Su)</strong></h3><p>At 5th level, the dollmaker can switch positions between himself and those he has connected to with his Phantasmal Strings as a move action. He does not provoke attacks of opportunity when he switches spaces with his construct. The dollmaker may use this ability up to 3 times per day + an additional time for every three necromancer levels after 5th.</p><p>This ability replaces fear aura.</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#guignol\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"yFGgevn3SujOCYYD","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"move","unchained":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductChargesCost":"","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":""}},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":""},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":"","damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":[],"attackNotes":[],"soundEffect":"","powerAttack":{"multiplier":"","damageBonus":2,"critMultiplier":1},"naturalAttack":{"primaryAttack":true,"secondary":{"attackBonus":"-5","damageMult":0.5}},"nonlethal":false,"manadamage":false,"touch":false,"usesAmmo":false,"spellEffect":"","spellArea":"","conditionals":[],"enh":{"value":null}}],"uses":{"per