{"name":"Phantasmal Strings (Su)","type":"buff","img":"icons/svg/ice-aura.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, as a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/pathfinder-basics/#standard\">standard action </a>, a dollmaker can infuse a construct creature within 30 feet with shadow energy. It gains a +1 profane bonus on all attack rolls and saving throws, as well as 1 temporary hit point per Hit Die and a +10 bonus to its movement speed. The bonus on attack rolls and saving throws increases by +1 for every five necromancer levels he possesses. These bonuses last for a number of rounds equal to half his necromancer level (minimum 1 round).</p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/necromancer/archetypes/dollmaker/#phantasmal-strings\">Link to Ability on FFd20 </a>This version updated on 02/18/2024</p><p>Set buff level to that of the dollmaker's class level</p>","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[{"_id":"DRjhTy9i","formula":"10","operator":"add","subTarget":"allSpeeds","modifier":"profane","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"p4ryX0CA","formula":"1+floor(@item.level/5)","operator":"add","subTarget":"attack","modifier":"profane","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"lD57Hh5G","formula":"1+floor(@item.level/5)","operator":"add","subTarget":"allSavingThrows","modifier":"profane","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"subType":"temp","active":false,"level":1,"duration":{"value":"max(1,floor(@item.level/2))","units":"round"},"hideFromToken":false,"uses":{"per":""}},"ownership":{"default":0,"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_5rvqcvuuap"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.2.7","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1709607516690,"modifiedTime":1709607888535,"lastModifi